{"tid":920941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"染髮劑過敏 少女毀容慘變「燈泡頭」","createTime":"2018-11-29T07:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T08:44:32.000Z","uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2477f5144c3e1c0072acbb50f046f5e932f0a5aa","tid":920941,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2018/11/29/1543482496_85122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2018%2F11%2F29%2F1543482496_85122.jpg&h=226d4893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只是染個髮，怎麼變成異形？英國一名19歲少女愛時髦，自行買染劑後DIY染髮，不久後頭皮爆癢，甚至頭部腫脹1倍，最後變成宛如「燈泡」形狀的臉型，且呼吸困難瀕死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2018/11/29/1543482377_27663.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2018%2F11%2F29%2F1543482377_27663.PNG&h=75ebdfbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，女學生埃斯特爾（Estelle）在法國留學，日前想變換新外型，買了一款DIY染髮劑，她興沖沖將染膏塗抹在亮麗秀髮上，豈料樂極生悲，由於埃斯特爾對染髮劑中的化學物質「對苯二胺」（p-Phenylenediamine，簡稱PPD）過敏，下場超嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n 一開始，埃斯特爾覺得頭皮發癢，隨後頭頂腫脹，然而她卻沒緊急就醫，反而跑去藥局買抗組胺藥和乳膏，希望能緩解症狀，隔日後更驚人，埃斯特爾的前額劇烈腫起，眼皮宛如長了大水泡般，甚至顴骨以上的部位更是朝左右邊突出，她形容「腦袋就像一個燈泡」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2018/11/29/1543482389_23034.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2018%2F11%2F29%2F1543482389_23034.PNG&h=176d0632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽媽驚覺不妙，趕緊將女兒送去急診室，醫師開立抗組胺藥和皮質類固醇後，但症狀卻沒好轉，埃斯特爾回憶，當時有如「被困在罐子裡的感覺」，翌日去另一間醫院救治，路途中她發現舌頭也開始腫脹且呼吸困難，性命垂危，醫師檢查後，趕快注射腎上腺素，才埃斯特爾保住性命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2018/11/29/1543482397_72097.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2018%2F11%2F29%2F1543482397_72097.PNG&h=2781adf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.news.ebc.net.tw/EbcNews/news/2018/11/29/1543482401_36566.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.news.ebc.net.tw%2FEbcNews%2Fnews%2F2018%2F11%2F29%2F1543482401_36566.PNG&h=122d45ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埃斯特爾從鬼門關前被救回，她心存感激，也坦承知道自己會對染劑過敏，當時染膏僅在皮膚測試30分鐘，沒乖乖等足48小時就魯莽染髮。事後埃斯特爾接受法媒《Le Parisien》採訪時，表示當下勉強還能看到東西，正在努力呼吸，希望把自己的慘痛經人，告誡大家「我幾乎死了，我不想讓其他人發生類似事情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HgiajBHmhFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHgiajBHmhFc&d=WoLvZM8B45wHJ3cTJ3oPmP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4d2d0d56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HgiajBHmhFc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/world/141539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2FNews%2Fworld%2F141539&d=WoLvZM8B45wHJ3cTJ3oPmP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4d4b6e11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/News/world/141539</a>"},{"pid":"05d1972b46ef6d1c5e77e91f8f0ee192c6a8c2b6","tid":920941,"uid":116905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:07:23.000Z","msg":"排隊落地獄揮手區<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ec58c2501010a1a53c6a19a4384a619b853fdb","tid":920941,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:08:56.000Z","msg":"小丸子入面果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3785955da883e4bbbe7d65782ea8724505a990e","tid":920941,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset